<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 7. Tetraclita singaporensis collected from (BUU 16. TC. TSG 02) from Na Tai beach, Phang-nga. A. Dorsal and ventral view of external shell, B. External (left panel) and internal (right panel) view of tergum (upper panel) and scutum (lower panel), C. Lateral side showing external surface of shell, D. Close up on the external surface of shell, E-H. Light microscopy on mouthparts, E. Labrum, E. Close up on the teeth of the labrum, G. Mandible, G. Close up on the pectinated lower margin of mandible. E-H. Scale bars in µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/117844" .

